owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-08-07t18:53:01z","updated_at":"2013-08-07t18:53:01z","body":"ok, @a-schild thank you for retesting and letting us know.\r\n\r\nnow can we get the coding experts on this? @bantu @ringmaster @vicdeo please help."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/22331946","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/2860#issuecomment-22331946","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2860","id":22331946,"user":{"login":"fekepp","id":5190990,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/8ebee32e7ac12cf544635a1e5903fc4f?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f4e345d9434bea0e74fe6e3df46f7527f.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"8ebee32e7ac12cf544635a1e5903fc4f","url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp","html_url":"https://github.com/fekepp","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-08-08t15:33:17z","updated_at":"2013-08-08t15:36:43z","body":"same issue here, currently 28247 files with 38gb in my user's trashbin and so far not able to clean them manually. so far ok for me in terms of disk space, but sometimes i like to clean-up :) oc takes currently 500gb on my server's disk.\r\n\r\nls -l files_trashbin/files/ | wc -l\r\n28247\r\n\r\ndu -hs files_trashbin/\r\n38g     files_trashbin/\r\n\r\n\r\nnot loading all items is of course required to not crash the browser. i don't know if its possible to keep the old directory structure? but still ppl could have thousands of files in a directory. also a queued maintenance task would be an option for the deletion of large file collections that asynchronous deletes the files when the user selects files for deletion (if not already the case)."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/22333567","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/2860#issuecomment-22333567","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2860","id":22333567,"user":{"login":"schiesbn","id":1589737,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/8912b598c7b32dd25b87fd168e0b06b2?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f0a323047dbe8329db30eae8dbe96e55e.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"8912b598c7b32dd25b87fd168e0b06b2","url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn","html_url":"https://github.com/schiesbn","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-08-08t15:54:57z","updated_at":"2013-08-08t15:54:57z","body":"if you delete the files with the web interface the folder structure is preserved. but with the sync client we get one delete request for every single file which results in such large file lists in the first place. see: https://github.com/owncloud/mirall/issues/612"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/22492747","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/2860#issuecomment-22492747","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2860","id":22492747,"user":{"login":"fekepp","id":5190990,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/8ebee32e7ac12cf544635a1e5903fc4f?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f4e345d9434bea0e74fe6e3df46f7527f.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"8ebee32e7ac12cf544635a1e5903fc4f","url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp","html_url":"https://github.com/fekepp","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-08-12t13:29:01z","updated_at":"2013-08-13t07:40:01z","body":"as a workaround you may temporary (or if you want permanent) set\r\n'trashbin_retention_obligation' => 1,\r\nin your config.php, documented here:\r\nhttp://doc.owncloud.org/server/5.0/user_manual/files/deletedfiles.html\r\n\r\nthis will trigger the files_trashbin app to delete files in your trashbin after one day which helped me to cleanup (i didn't test the behaviour if you set it to zero). default is 180 days/50% of available free disk space.\r\n\r\ni am not sure if it is triggered by the regular cron jobs (which it should because many ppl don't use the frontend to handle files, like me) or just when you delete an item in the web frontend. it blocks the user interface while deleting the files which took a long time (~1h/20k files) in this case. access with another browser at the same time was possible.\r\n\r\nit also triggers a lot of\r\n{\"app\":\"php\",\"message\":\"filesize(): stat failed for path_to_file_in_trashbin at \\/var\\/www\\/owncloud\\/lib\\/files\\/storage\\/local.php#74\",\"level\":2,\"time\":1376314904}\r\nerrors logged in at log level 2. maybe worth another bug.\r\n"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/22494107","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/2860#issuecomment-22494107","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2860","id":22494107,"user":{"login":"schiesbn","id":1589737,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/8912b598c7b32dd25b87fd168e0b06b2?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f0a323047dbe8329db30eae8dbe96e55e.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"8912b598c7b32dd25b87fd168e0b06b2","url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn","html_url":"https://github.com/schiesbn","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-08-12t13:49:22z","updated_at":"2013-08-12t13:50:37z","body":"@fekepp the trash bin expire old files every time a file gets deleted and every time we overstep the max size if a new file gets added to your owncloud. this is completely independent from the interface you use (web, mobile client, desktop client or plain webdav)"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/22494449","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/2860#issuecomment-22494449","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2860","id":22494449,"user":{"login":"fekepp","id":5190990,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/8ebee32e7ac12cf544635a1e5903fc4f?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f4e345d9434bea0e74fe6e3df46f7527f.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"8ebee32e7ac12cf544635a1e5903fc4f","url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp","html_url":"https://github.com/fekepp","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fekepp/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-08-12t13:54:32z","updated_at":"2013-08-12t13:54:32z","body":"sounds good. my case was also a bit artificial because i triggered the permanent deletion of 20k+ files at the same time with the new configuration."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/22546288","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/2860#issuecomment-22546288","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2860","id":22546288,"user":{"login":"a-schild","id"